            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>Publius Crittius Firmus, son of Publius, of tribe Cornelia, first-spear of the 22nd Legion, tribune of the 6th cohort of the watchmen, prefect of the camps of the 12th Legion Fulminata, quattuorvir with judicial authority, flamen of the divine Augustus; Crittia Priscilla, son of Publius, flaminica of Agrippina Augusta; Caius Crittius Firmus, the son, son of Publius, of tribe Cornelia.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The characters in the funerary monument are likely father, daughter and son, and the family is elsewhere attested in Aeclanum (CIL 9.1064, 1173).</p> 
            </div>
